CostaClick,is,the,professional,portal,for,travel,agents,provided,by,Costa,Cruises,a,booking,service,for,cruises,around,the,world,The,CostaClick,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,a,huge,variety,of,information,from,the,portal,via,SOAP,calls,Users,can,search,for,cruises,by,origin,destination,ship,and,or,port,They,can,also,retrieve,a,full,cruise,description,as,well,as,the,documents,required,for,booking,On,top,of,that,users,can,also,retrieve,information,on,special,services,for,a,cruise,fares,ports,and,much,more